videoScript.text: Whoa, OpenAI has some serious competition.
It's DeepSeek AI, a challenger from China. DeepSeek's models are incredibly powerful
and get this, more affordable. They even beat OpenAI in some reasoning tests. Can you believe it?
Plus, DeepSeek is focused on explainable AI and data privacy. That's amazing.
So are you team OpenAI or are you ready to DeepSeek? Let me know in the comments.
